tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE factory_production_data (
    factory_id INT,
    production_date DATE,
    product_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    defect_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE Production_Records (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    factory_id INT,
    production_date DATE,
    produced_quantity INT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_factory_id FOREIGN KEY (factory_id) REFERENCES Factory_Information(factory_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Quality_Checks (
    check_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    record_id INT,
    defect_type VARCHAR(255),
    severity INT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_record_id FOREIGN KEY (record_id) REFERENCES Production_Records(record_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Factory_A (
    factory_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    production_date DATE,
    product_type VARCHAR(50),
    quantity INT,
    worker_id INT
);
